## BaseClient.nextSN property

The `SN` number of the next `callApi()`<!-- -->, which can be passed to `abort()` to abort an API request.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
get nextSN(): number;
```

## Example


```ts
let nextSN = client.nextSN;
client.callApi('xxx', { value: 'xxx' })

```
